title: Life Isn't Always Sunshine and Rainbows: Winter Break Recap, School, How I'm Feeling
itunes:title: Life Isn't Always Sunshine and Rainbows: Winter Break Recap, School, How I'm Feeling
description:
In this solo episode with Danielle, she gets deep into everything relating to her life. She touches on how winter break is going, family life, grades, getting hate comments, boys, and just about everything in between! Let's get ~real~.
